cepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null},{"id":3285815,"name":"","username":"GearFox","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/www.chiefdelphi.com/gearfox/{size}/191322_2.png","created_at":"2024-01-16T17:20:50.477Z","cooked":"<p>Two things before I even take a good look through code:</p>
<ol>
<li>any time you’re posting raw code in <span class="abbreviation">CD<template class="tooltiptext" data-text="Chief Delphi"></template></span> (or on discord), put “```” before and after the code block to make it easier for everyone else to read</li>
